{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Language Immersion:</strong> Newcomer is a language immersion experience for beginners to<strong>\u00a0</strong>learn and practice 9 languages:</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Latin-American Spanish</strong></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>French</strong></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Italian</strong></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>German</strong></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Castilian Spanish</strong></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Brazilian Portuguese</strong></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Turkish</strong></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Dutch</strong></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Tagalog</strong></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Results:</strong> In your adventure, you will:</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">learn and communicate fundamental survival phrases with a variety of in-game NPCs</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">gain exposure to thousands of new words </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">start to identify correct pronunciation </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">learn beginner vocabulary</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">encounter grammar naturally</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">As a Newcomer, you are given a <u>phrasebook</u> and a quest...  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2063790/extras/PhrasebookGifEnglish.gif?t=1733431461\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">You encounter target language speakers and <u>start to communicate</u> using basic phrases...</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2063790/extras/BeginnerConversationGif.gif?t=1733431461\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Your ability to <u>translate</u> your target language makes it possible to understand your new language... </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2063790/extras/ChunkTranslationEnglishGif.gif?t=1733431461\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">As you travel through new areas, you <u>review vocabulary by battling</u> hostile creatures... </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2063790/extras/BattleEnglishGif.gif?t=1733431461\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">You start using your new language to <u>complete conversation tasks</u> by discussing a variety of people, places, and things within the world... </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2063790/extras/TaskCompletionEnglishGif.gif?t=1733431461\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">You level up and <u>unlock new words and phrases</u>, enabling you to engage in deeper and more nuanced conversations... </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2063790/extras/LevelUpEnglishGif.gif?t=1733431461\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">You start to utilize <u>intelligent translations</u> which explain individual words in more detail... </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2063790/extras/IntelligentTranslationEnglishGif.gif?t=1733431461\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Your new language takes you to many parts of the <u>open world</u>... </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2063790/extras/ExploreNewAreasGif.gif?t=1733431461\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Ultimately, you must learn your second language to <u>defeat the Dark Crimson</u>... </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2063790/extras/DarkCrimsonEnglishGif.gif?t=1733431461\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Play and continue the same adventure on your PC and mobile (Android, iOS) device... </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2063790/extras/CrossSaveGif.gif?t=1733431461\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Play and learn many languages... </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2063790/extras/ManyGamesGif.gif?t=1733431461\" /></p>","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2063790/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1733431461","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2063790/page.bg.jpg?t=1733431461","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2063790/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1733431461","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2063790/capsule_184x69.jpg?t=1733431461","categories":[{"description":"Single-player","id":2}],"content_descriptors":{"ids":[],"notes":null},"detailed_description":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Language Immersion:</strong> Newcomer is a language immersion experience for beginners to<strong>\u00a0</strong>learn and practice 9 languages:</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Latin-American Spanish</strong></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>French</strong></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Italian</strong></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>German</strong></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Castilian Spanish</strong></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Brazilian Portuguese</strong>